name.value: Case Based Surveillance Age at Case Investigation

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the age at case investigation of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Binational Reporting Criteria

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the Binational Reporting Criteria of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Case Notification Panel Profile

description.value: Defines constraints on Observation to represent the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Case Outbreak

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the Case Outbreak section of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Cause of Death Profile

description.value: Defines constraints on on the Observation resource for supporting public health reporting workflows involving the cause of death of the subject.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Composition Profile

description.value: Defines constraints to the Composition resource in order to meet the needs of public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Date of Initial Report

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the date of initial report on the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Date of First Report to Public Health Department

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the date reported of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Document Profile

description.value: Defines a document type bundle that contains all related profiles.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Earliest Date Reported

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the earliest date reported of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Earliest Date Reported to State

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the earliest date reported to the state of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Exposure Observation Profile

description.value: Defines constraints to the CBS Case Notification Panel Member profile to represent the exposure observations of the case notification panel.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Immediate National Notifiable Condition

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the imemdiate national notifiable condition of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Case Investigation Start Date

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the case investigation start date of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Jurisdiction Code

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the jurisdiction code of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Morbidity and Mortality Weekly Report (MMWR) Elements

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the MMWR elements of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance National Reporting Jurisdiction

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the national reporting jurisdiction of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Pregnancy Status

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the pregnancy status of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Questionnaire Profile

description.value: Defines constraints on the Questionnaire resource to set the minimum expected details to be provided as part of case based surveillance program's questionnaire/survey data.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Reporting County

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the reporting county of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Reporting State

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the reporting state of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Social Determinants of Health Profile

description.value: Defines constraints on the Observation resource to capture subject's Social Determinants of Health in order to meet the needs of public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Specimen Profile

description.value: Defines constraints on the Specimen resource in order to meet the needs of public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Transmission Mode

description.value: Defines constraints on CBS Case Notification Panel to represent the transmission mode of the case notification panel in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Subject Vaccinated per ACIP Recommendations Profile

description.value: Defines constraints on the Observation resource to capture whether subject was vaccinated per ACIP Recommendations in order to meet the needs of public health surveillance programs.

name.value: US Case Based Surveillance Condition of Interest Profile

description.value: Defines constraints and extensions to the Condition resource in order to meet the needs of public health surveillance programs, further constrainting the US Core based ECR US Public Health profiles.

name.value: US Case Based Surveillance Hospitalization Encounter Profile

description.value: Defines constraints on the ECR US Public Health Encounter to represent hospitalization due to a condition of interest for public health case based surveillance programs.

name.value: US Case Based Surveillance Immunization Profile

description.value: Defines further constraints on the US Core Immunization profile to capture subject vaccination records in order to meet the needs of public health surveillance programs.

name.value: US Case Based Surveillance Lab Diagnostic Report

description.value: Defines a DiagnosticReport resource profile in order to meet the needs of public health surveillance programs.

name.value: US Case Based Surveillance Lab Observation

description.value: Defines constraints on the Observation resource in order to meet the needs of lab reporting in public health surveillance programs.

name.value: US Case Based Surveillance Patient Profile

description.value: Defines further constraints and extensions to the ECR US Public Health profile in order to meet the needs of case based surveillance programs while maintaining adherence to US Core standards.

name.value: US Case Based Surveillance Performing Laboratory Profile

description.value: Defines further constraints and extensions to the ECR US Public Health Organization profile in order to meet the needs of case based surveillance programs while maintaining adherence to US Core standards.

name.value: US Case Based Surveillance Reporting Source Organization Profile

description.value: Defines constraints to the Organization resource in order to meet the needs of public health surveillance programs regarding the reporting source.

name.value: US Case Based Surveillance Travel History Profile

description.value: Defines constraints on the ECR US PH Travel History profile to capture additional data in order to meet the needs of public health case based surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance CDC Address Use Extension

description.value: Indicates the use of the address as per information surveillance program.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Case Class Status

description.value: A code denoting the status of the case/event as suspect, probable, confirmed, or not a case per CSTE/CDC/surveillance case definitions.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Specimen Role Extension

description.value: Indicates the role of the sample.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Illness Duration

description.value: Illness duration to obscure PHII in place of absokute dates.

name.value: US Case Based Surveillance Program Specific Time Window

description.value: Time window of interest in relationship to a specified event as determined by individual case based surveillance programs.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance Related Case Extension

description.value: A list of strings with relevant case numbers and a type element that specifies the nature of the relation.

name.value: US Case Based Surveillance Period and Mode of Travel Extension

description.value: An extension capturing the circumstances of travel to a destination.

name.value: Additional codes for Address.use.

description.value: Codes for Address.use which are used as slice discriminators to capture address history at relevant points in time to case surveillance.

name.value: CBS Case Notification Panel Value Set

description.value: Codes found in the case notification panel that are otherwise not captured in other CBS profiles.

name.value: Combined ValueSet for Lab DiagnosticReport Code.

description.value: Codes for Lab Test Type. The codes are from two PHINVADS valuesets to support labs test repeating group

name.value: CBS Related Case Type Value Set

description.value: Codes found in the case notification panel that are otherwise not captured in other CBS profiles.

name.value: STD Sexual History and Drug Use Questionnaire Panel

description.value: This is an example valueset for how to setup coding for an Epi Questionnaire Panel using a selection of codes from the STD MMG.

name.value: CBS Case Social Determinants of Health Category Value Set

description.value: Categories for social determinants of health and related elements of social history which may be captured in the SDOH profile.

name.value: CBS Case Social Determinants of Health Codes Value Set

description.value: Codes for social determinants of health and related elements of social history which may be captured in the SDOH profile.

name.value: CBS Time Window Relative To Value Set

description.value: Codes for specific resource elements referenced by the CBS Program Specific Time Window extension, to convey to which element in the referenced resource a time window is relative.

name.value: Case Based Surveillance temporary/placeholder code system.

description.value: Code system defined as placeholders for items that are not defined in existing systems.
